race.description: Place A Srm With Bet Nation 1-3 Wins H
race.comment: BINDI BOODIE (2) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (22.15) at this track in a Grade 5. Lines up from box 2 for the first time. Deserves serious consideration. PANAMA LOCO (1) goes very well here starting nine times for three wins and three minors. Placed last time (22.10) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 1.75 lengths. Looks a key chance on best figures. ROYAL BLOOD (3) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing third (21.93) at this track in a Grade 5 over 380m. Expected to be in the finish again. HOLLYWOOD DIVA (8) won as expected last time and another big run is on the cards.
